{"tid":1831180,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"第二十六屆香港電影評論學會大獎得獎名單","createTime":"2020-01-20T08:05:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T07:23:39.000Z","uid":4260,"like":12,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"54e45e0bc9457d5b81b802d911fa7ea723ef46af","tid":1831180,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:05:40.000Z","msg":"最佳男演員︰劉俊謙《幻愛》 太保《叔&middot;叔》<br />\n最佳女演員︰蔡思韵《幻愛》<br />\n最佳電影 ︰《叔&middot;叔》<br />\n最佳導演 ︰曾國祥《少年的你》<br />\n最佳編劇 ︰黃綺琳《金都》"},{"pid":"a68e76d245317bd6622b051536d56d161133dc8b","tid":1831180,"uid":132587,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:07:13.000Z","msg":"曾國藩收一收皮啦好嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6012f65d487dc776a191683a867c2dddf407d76","tid":1831180,"uid":4260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:08:03.000Z","msg":"<strong>【本土作品抬頭】電影評論學會大獎新人湧現 劉俊謙太保同獲最佳男演員</strong><br />\n<br />\n第26屆香港電影評論學會今日公佈得獎名單，近年新晉導演及演員湧現，得獎名單亦反映這點事實（見附表），5個大獎新人取其中4。最佳男演員今年鬧雙胞，演過ViuTV劇集《教束》劉俊謙憑周冠威導演作品《幻愛》奪得，另一位男演員得主是羸過金馬獎最佳男配角的太保（原名張嘉年），憑《叔&middot;叔》贏得。<br />\n<br />\n現年25歲的蔡思韵憑《幻愛》成最佳女演員，她之前演出過台灣電影《返校》，戲中演一名老師。劉俊謙跟蔡思韵因為合作《幻》片戲假情真，發展成情侶，他們將有機會拍拖出席3月舉行的頒獎儀式。<br />\n<br />\n最佳電影獎得主為《叔&middot;叔》，導演楊曜愷是回流香港拍戲的新導演。最佳編劇獎由黃綺琳的《金都》奪得，本片是她首部導演作品，《金》片是靠贏得「首部劇情計劃」的資金開拍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200120&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=60503490\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200120%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D60503490&d=%2F7nbYOXxgzDTTn%2FAx8VV9wZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=29dde967\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200120%26s%3D7018882%26a%3D60503490&h=692eef86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200120&amp;s=7018882&amp;a=60503490</a>"},{"pid":"dbc4649ad7dd9937f90e65a811b29142e5a1d9b2","tid":1831180,"uid":48479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:13:07.000Z","msg":"蘋果搶先公佈賽果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過未有推薦電影名單"},{"pid":"a2cb6773d525c0f4c6a30a62be30be09d774ecd5","tid":1831180,"uid":4260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200120/large/1579503337_e1cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200120%2Flarge%2F1579503337_e1cd.jpg&h=62559d33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蔡思韵因與陳奕迅合作ViuTV劇集《短暫的婚姻》打響名氣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200120/large/1579503337_2815.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200120%2Flarge%2F1579503337_2815.jpg&h=0aede4f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉俊謙於ViuTV劇集《教束》演出備受觀眾讚揚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200120/large/1579503333_7d5c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200120%2Flarge%2F1579503333_7d5c.jpg&h=d68eefa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《幻愛》由《十年》導演之一周冠威執導。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200120/large/1579503333_ffde.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200120%2Flarge%2F1579503333_ffde.jpg&h=c80d61c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n劉俊謙與蔡思韵因為合作《幻愛》戲假情真，發展成情侶。（IG圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200120/large/1579503335_9355.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200120%2Flarge%2F1579503335_9355.jpg&h=ec9c7c02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《金都》以太子金都大廈講述香港男女面對婚姻的糾結。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200120/large/1579503335_365a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200120%2Flarge%2F1579503335_365a.jpg&h=397612fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾國祥憑《少年的你》撇甩曾「志偉之子」之稱，導演功力被業內讚賞。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200120/large/1579503336_b2b7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200120%2Flarge%2F1579503336_b2b7.jpg&h=b11d0a50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《叔&middot;叔》講述一對香港中老年同性戀的故事。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等睇學會post得獎理由撮要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"634976bea24d8829e7c0b24f1b472b0d666b3992","tid":1831180,"uid":236359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:14:31.000Z","msg":"劉俊謙 上位啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89911e8142e066b5666d14ef28fde0fe0e421e03","tid":1831180,"uid":236359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:16:28.000Z","msg":"成班扮支持港產片去左邊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d163e0b19e7a362cb315c050f9ea7f639763c73d","tid":1831180,"uid":64953,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:16:52.000Z","msg":"劉俊謙又高大又靚仔又好戲<br />\n蔡思韵真係好好命<br />\n利申 非gay"},{"pid":"77b1a93e3ffcb1d539961c1914b6da51cee648ae","tid":1831180,"uid":38572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:24:18.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"8c819d411e28e457d5f475f4c2a2be0fe6cc14fc","tid":1831180,"uid":247203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T08:32:31.000Z","msg":"番香港睇幻愛先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8285e5913c568103cf8ef4819e6e8e8b8a5317de","tid":1831180,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c819d411e28e457d5f475f4c2a2be0fe6cc14fc","tid":1831180,"uid":247203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB